cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA 

This paper deals with computational imaging, sensing, and low-level computer vision, which are all sub-fields of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a framework for infusing knowledge of image formation into deep networks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses iterative optimization methods, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper presents results for compressed sensing magnetic resonance imaging (MRI), which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
